---
description: Build system — always use task commands, never raw docker buildx
globs: docker-bake.hcl,meta-secret/Dockerfile,Taskfile.yml,meta-secret/**/*.toml
alwaysApply: true
---

### Build entry point (mandatory)

- build config: `docker-bake.hcl` (targets, cache, tags)
- all stages: `meta-secret/Dockerfile` (single multi-stage file)
- **always run builds via `task <target>` from repo root — never `docker buildx bake`, `docker buildx build`, or `docker build`**
- after updating any `Cargo.toml`, run `task generate-recipe`
- read `.ai/skills/build-via-task/SKILL.md` before any build/test shell command

### Pre-command gate

If your next command matches `docker buildx` or `docker build` → **stop** and use `task` (or add a task to `Taskfile.yml` first).

### Task commands

| Action | Command |
|---|---|
| Run tests | `task test` |
| Warm Rust test cache | `task warm-cache` |
| Warm WASM dep cache | `task warm-cache-wasm` |
| Build all images | `task build` |
| Build + push | `task push` |
| Build meta-server | `task meta-server` |
| Build web image | `task web` |
| Export web dist locally | `task web-local` |
| Export wasm pkg locally | `task wasm-local` |
| Update cargo chef recipe | `task generate-recipe` |
| Run web-ui locally | `task web-run` |
| Playwright smoke tests | `PLAYWRIGHT_BASE_URL=… task playwright-test` |
| Add shadcn-vue component | `cd meta-secret/web-cli/ui && npx shadcn-vue@latest add <name>` |

Full list: `task -l`
